      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Alurea was a very peaceful place until a creepy clown decided to take over. He got together all his beastie buddies and attacked Alurea! Now, the lands are filled with monsters of all kinds! It's time to win back Alurea! Get'em, boys!",
